## Additional Terms for Unity Assets

This license applies to the source code and documentation. Unity assets,
third-party plugins, and external resources may have separate licenses.
Please refer to individual asset documentation for specific license terms.

### Procedural Music System

The procedural music system code (Assets/Scripts/Audio/*) is available
under the MIT license. The generated audio output and musical compositions
created by the system are not subject to licensing restrictions.

